com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.outputs

Class GoogleCloudStorageFileOutputWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.OutputWriter<ByteBuffer>
      • com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.outputs.GoogleCloudStorageFileOutputWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class GoogleCloudStorageFileOutputWriter
extends OutputWriter<ByteBuffer>
    An OutputWriter that writes bytes to a GCS file that it creates. Produces a single file output (usually on a per-shard basis). This format does not insert any separator characters, so it by default cannot be read back with the CloudStorageLineInputReader.
    See Also:
